column5: Please welcome a new sponsor to our community. Click HERE to browse their site. Their banner has been added to the rotation at the upper right of the screen.  Thanks and welcome aboard Mako. I'm sure you'll provide us with great BOQ information.  OFC administration team.
Let me check....it works for me Dan.
You have the magic touch it's working now, thanks  Edit: Awesome site!
Thanks Roy for the plug,  Adding the finishing touches to the site, and just put up a contest with a sweet prize for all the Bay of Quinte walleye hunters.  Cheers  www.fishingbayofquinte.com
Good looking site so far Mako, looking forward to your updates.  Check out my entry
Roy, Mako, still having problems with the site. Getting "domain not found".
I always get the site no problems, John. I'll get in touch with him in case he hasn't seen this. Thanks.
Just tried it again now and it works fine. Wonder if the site was down off and on for updates?
Could be, John. New sites sometimes have tiny glitches to work out. Why even established sites have problems eh? (wink wink, nudge nudge)
